data.name: label7.Text
data.value: .gz files are typically located at: C:\Documents and Settings\WINLOGINNAME\Application Data\SecondLife\cache Show hidden files must be enabled to see this directory. After browsing to a .gz or .inv, a temporary .inv is created in the SLMIV installation inv folder.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value: NOTE: When backing-up, this screen may appear 'Not Responding' but is actually working. On the My Inventory tab, you may always right-click on an item and choose Download and Save to perform faster individual backups.
